-- Venezuela Socialist Party Chooses Cabello for Head of Assembly
-- B y   C o r i n a   P o n s   a n d   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2013-01-05T17:53:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-05/venezuela-socialist-party-chooses-cabello-for-head-of-assembly.html
Venezuela ’s ruling party will back
Diosdado Cabello to remain as president of the National Assembly
today, paving the way for him to take over the government should
President  Hugo Chavez  be declared too ill to remain head of
state.  The United Socialist Party of Venezuela unanimously chose
Cabello to be their sole candidate for the post, ensuring his
victory in today’s vote in congress where they have the majority
of seats, lawmaker Fernando Soto Rojas said on state TV.  To contact the reporter on this story:
